CustomField.description: Used in reporting to calculate the "Actual Traveltime" for each Service Appointment. The calculation is based on the "Actual Start" date/time and the "Travel Start" date/time and returns the result in minutes.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Travel Time is calculated from "Travel Start" to "Actual Start" (=Onsite).
CustomField.label: Actual Travel Time (Minutes)
